    <div class="pp-box pp-box-style1 pp-dashboard-box" style="height:220;">
      <h2 class="pp-dashboard-feedback">Support &amp; Feedback</h2>
      <p>Something broken? Something missing? Tell us about it now!</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#" class="pp-textlink pp-bullet" onclick=" if (window.UserVoice) {UserVoice.Popin.show()}; return false;"> 
            Feedback</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>Need help? Have questions? Send us an email:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#" class="pp-textlink pp-bullet" onClick="Paperpile.utils.openURL('mailto:support@paperpile.org');">support@paperpile.org</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
